The '''Policy and Resources Council''' or '''P and R''' was a council of the [[Galactic Alliance Senate]]. It passed an amendment, numbered [[Item 357]] that secretly allowed [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] to change more laws without the approval of the Senate, eventually creating a [[Triumvirate (Galactic Alliance)|triumvirate]]. On that day, 563 changes were proposed, including [[Item 24]] and [[Item 358]].

